  "remarks": "Passport no.: Saudi Arabian passport number F654645, issued on 30 Apr. 2005 , expired on 7 Mar. 2010. Issue date in Hijri Calendar 24/06/1426. Expiry date in Hijri Calendar 21/03/1431.  National identification no.: Saudi Arabian civil identification number 1028745097.  Operative and principal bomb maker of Al-Qaida in the Arabian Peninsula (AQAP) (QE.A.129.10.). Believed to be hiding in Yemen as at Mar. 2011. Wanted by Saudi Arabia.Reportedly deceased. INTERPOL Orange Notice (file #2009/52/OS/CCC, #81) has been issued for him. Also associated with Nasir 'abd-al-Karim 'Abdullah Al-Wahishi (deceased), Qasim Yahya Mahdi al-Rimi (QI.A.282.10.), and Anwar Nasser Abdulla Al-Aulaqi (QI.A.283.10.) (deceased). Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 15 November 2021. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 8 November 2022.\n  "
